headline: AIG to Report Third Quarter 2025 Financial Results on November 4, 2025, and Host Conference Call on November 5, 2025
summary: NEW YORK, October 09, 2025--American International Group, Inc. (NYSE: AIG) will report financial results for the third quarter ended September 30, 2025, after the market closes on Tuesday, November 4, 2025. AIG’s press release and financial supplement will be available in the Investors section of AIG’s website at https://www.aig.com.

headline: Will AIG’s (AIG) Leadership Reshuffle Mark a Turning Point for Management Credibility?
summary: American International Group, Inc. recently announced the retirement of Don Bailey, Executive Vice President and CEO of North America Commercial Insurance, effective at year-end, and detailed a new leadership structure for its North America operations to take effect January 1, 2026. This transition brings experienced leaders into new roles and reflects AIG’s efforts to strengthen organizational stability and continuity within its key commercial insurance business.
